夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=c8249e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=131f7344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"fd62c3c9784467143ae5499cad1a0540f7530a0d","tid":1450624,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:48:31.000Z","msg":"機場文宣整合post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450351</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"db075d8a95fb49d0d4459dd862b2518a2c8f21d6","tid":1450624,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24d400c158bf697f8de2dba8b97fc1713d07cf30","tid":1450624,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJ86KfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJ86KfQ.jpg&h=a75927e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ma0dpfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fma0dpfQ.jpg&h=09641521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKsWm2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKsWm2w.jpg&h=4985f15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cX4Bm2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/